{"id": 2116, "genre": 1000, "title": "如果一定要拍“大女主”戏，你觉得它应该往哪些方向使劲儿？", "description": "是真的在女性话题上有态度，还是只为了迎合女观众做点表面功夫？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 15867, "comment_count": 37, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180111175326yf0qtJ4xGLgmNFl7.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-01-14T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3554, "title": "如果一定要拍“大女主”戏，你觉得它应该往哪些方向使劲儿？", "content": "如果一定要拍“大女主戏”，你觉得它应该往哪些方向使劲儿？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 258871, "content": "来一份女主奋斗史，多加奋斗，少强调美貌和出身", "image": "img/option/option/201801121401197ZKIsTUx3SivNeuG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 258872, "content": "不把女主爱上谁、和谁结婚当故事情节的主要推动力", "image": "img/option/option/201801121402179eGDSUodksvZTCwQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 258873, "content": "展现女主在不同年龄段的闪光点，不要只突出年轻活力", "image": "img/option/option/20180112140442fy2pTcCqNgImWPM5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 258874, "content": "其他女性角色也有丰富形象，不只是陪衬", "image": "img/option/option/20180112140824vBIwFozsTCAj5tmn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 258875, "content": "帮女主治治作天作地的公主病", "image": "img/option/option/20180112141724KH30OxFVjo1hXAmg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 258876, "content": "给她一个丰富立体的人格，而不是天真无脑傻白甜", "image": "img/option/option/20180112142048AKoVUX4xYgzqlpmL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 258877, "content": "不把女性角色的单身当不完美或一个问题", "image": "img/option/option/20180112142154s3v8MqReFtZUHojI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 259203, "content": "把男性角色拍成正常人，而不是一见钟情无脑支持女主", "image": "img/option/option/20180114172038iq2HahybPQGLS6Ct.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}